'''国防学院'''（National Defence Academy，缩写：NDA）是印度[[普纳|普纳]]的一所军校，培养海陆空三军军官。该校的学生已有三人获得[[Param_Vir_Chakra|Param Vir Chakra]]勋章，也有多位校友担任印度海、陆、空三军参谋长，使其成为印度负有盛名的军校之一。<ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/for-second-time-in-history-all-three-chiefs-to-be-from-same-nda-course-13193|title=For second time in history, all three Chiefs to be from same NDA course|last=Mohan|first=Vijay|date=17 December 2019|website=Tribune India|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191217183326/https://www.tribuneindia.com/news/for-second-time-in-history-all-three-chiefs-to-be-from-same-nda-course-13193|archive-date=2019-12-17|access-date=2019-12-18|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref Name="NDA">{{cite web|url=http://nda.nic.in/chief-of-staff.html|title=:: Welcome to National Defence Academy ::|publisher=nda.nic.in|accessdate=10 December 2013|archive-date=2019-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190818040757/https://nda.nic.in/chief-of-staff.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==校区==
[[File:Aerial_view_of_the_National_Defence_Academy,_Pune.jpg|thumb]]
其校区位于普纳市中心西南17公里的Khadakwasla区，东南面有一个湖泊，停靠着用来训练学生的军舰HMS Angostura。
